      <title>澳大利亚监管机构设立新部门，加强对私人市场的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/australia-regulator-steps-up-private-markets-focus-with-new-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们对该行业估值持续担忧的背景下，澳大利亚企业监管机构已成立专门部门，负责在未来 12 个月内与私人市场进行接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/australia-regulator-steps-up-private-markets-focus-with-new-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 01:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
