    <item>
      <title>印度提高税收以抑制股票交易中的零售狂热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度几十年来首次对股票投资和股票衍生品收益税做出重大修改，试图抑制该国 5 万亿美元市场的投机交易激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默瑟称美国大选白热化加大美联储维持利率不变的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/heated-us-election-lifts-chances-of-fed-on-hold-mercer-cio-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美世有限责任公司 (Mercer LLC) 首席投资官表示，美联储维持利率不变直至年底的可能性越来越大，而不是卷入日益激烈的美国大选竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/heated-us-election-lifts-chances-of-fed-on-hold-mercer-cio-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
